---------------------------------------------------
[spell]: Soul Crush
[level]: 3rd Lvl Necromancy
[cost] : 2/3 Necr sp
[type] : damage
[delay]: none
---------------------------------------------------
The powerful Soulcrush spell will drain the
remaining life from your victim.  The intended
target must already be near death for this spell
to work.  The higher the casters Necromancy skill
the more powerful this spell will be.
---------------------------------------------------

